\"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike in multiple upstream services\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟从正常的10,000ms增加到异常期间的918,871ms及更高\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"propagation of delays from productcatalogservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用productcatalogservice的延迟达到异常的6,071,905ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些异常可能需要对 `productcatalogservice` 的性能进行调优，或者检查其与其他服务或数据库的交互。"}
